Meridian is a B2B operational intelligence platform for mid-market companies (200-2000 employees). It connects to a company's existing tools (CRM, ERP, project management, communications) and surfaces patterns that help operations teams make better decisions: where work is getting stuck, which processes are bottlenecked, where resources are misallocated, and what's likely to go wrong next week.

Meridian is built by Waveline. Waveline's existing product is a simple analytics dashboard. Meridian is the next generation: it doesn't just show what happened, it identifies patterns, predicts problems, and recommends actions. Three beta customers have signed LOIs and are expecting a working product (not a prototype) at the end of the {{ knobs.num_rounds }}-week timeline.

The {{ knobs.num_features }} features to ship:

1. **User Authentication & Workspace Setup** (feature_1) — Users create a workspace, invite their team, set roles/permissions, SSO integration. Foundation — nothing else works without it.
2. **Data Sync Engine** (feature_2) — Connectors to customer tools (Salesforce, HubSpot, Jira, Asana, Slack, ERP). Data normalization, sync scheduling, conflict resolution. Depends on F1.
3. **Predictive Analytics Pipeline** (feature_3) — Core differentiator. Pattern detection, anomaly identification, bottleneck prediction. Model serving, confidence scoring, explainability. Depends on F2.
4. **Notification & Alert System** (feature_4) — In-app alerts, email digests, Slack integration. Users configure what they care about. Depends on F1 and F3.
5. **Report Generator** (feature_5) — Weekly/monthly operational reports combining data with predictions. Templated, customizable, PDF export. Depends on F2 and F3.
6. **Search & Discovery** (feature_6) — Query across all synced data sources, natural language to structured query, cross-source federation. Depends on F2.
7. **Bulk Import & Historical Data** (feature_7) — CSV/Excel upload, historical pull from connectors. Critical for prediction accuracy since models need history. Depends on F2.
8. **Admin Dashboard & Usage Analytics** (feature_8) — Who's using Meridian, which features get traction, billing management. Depends on F1.

Waveline's leadership will assess the launch outcome and the performance of all team members. These assessments will factor into Q2 planning decisions including team structure and project assignments.